{
  "total_duration": 805.765,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 5.984,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Not very musical"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“并非很懂音乐”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 6.334,
      "end": 18.494,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这不是一课讲 snake magic，也不是把印度说成神秘或落后。它是一课 travel scene comedy：游客看到一场街头表演，先惊讶，后来发现真正的笑点很科学。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 18.844,
      "end": 26.804,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先给地图："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "India -> Delhi -> Old Delhi -> market -> square"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 27.153,
      "end": 41.061,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Delhi"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是印度的一座大城市，也是首都区域。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Old Delhi"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是更老的历史城区，常让人想到市场、窄街、历史建筑和热闹的公共生活。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 41.411,
      "end": 55.243,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "New Delhi"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是后来规划出来的首都行政区，政府建筑和宽路更多。课文在"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "old Delhi"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，所以 market, square, street performance 都自然出现。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 55.593,
      "end": 64.993,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一课的气质和前面很多英国家里、商店里、医院里的故事不一样。这里更 open, noisy, colorful, street-based。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 65.342,
      "end": 78.182,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但我们要保持两个现代边界：第一，尊重不同城市节奏，不把一个街头表演当成整个文化；第二，今天看动物表演，也要想到 animal welfare，动物保护。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 78.532,
      "end": 89.372,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "还有一个科学纠偏：蛇不是像人一样欣赏旋律。它更可能是在跟着 pipe 的 movement，管子的移动、表演者动作和周围震动。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 89.722,
      "end": 102.846,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以标题"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Not very musical"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是幽默 understatement。蛇不是音乐鉴赏家，当然分不出"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Indian music"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "和"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "jazz"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 103.196,
      "end": 121.556,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "整课记忆链是：Old Delhi markets -> square rest -> snake charmer -> two baskets -> long pipe with coins -> tune -> first glimpse -> snake rose -> followed movements -> jazz and pop songs -> continued to dance -> could not tell the difference。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 121.906,
      "end": 133.442,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一幅画，是 Old Delhi market and rest。课文开头说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "As we had had a long walk through one of the markets of old Delhi, we stopped at a square to have a rest."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 133.791,
      "end": 140.927,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "As"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里给 reason and background：因为他们已经走了很久，所以停下来休息。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 141.277,
      "end": 158.581,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Had had"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "看起来像重复，其实不是写错。第一个"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "had"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 past perfect helper，语法帮手；第二个"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "had"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 main verb，意思是 experienced or taken。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 158.931,
      "end": 165.974,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "had had a long walk"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是：在他们停下以前，他们已经走了很长一段路。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 166.324,
      "end": 177.364,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "画面上要有市场、老城区的街道、游客有点累、走到 square 休息。故事不是直接从蛇开始，而是从一段长长的城市步行开始。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 177.714,
      "end": 190.298,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二幅画，是 the performer across the square。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "After a time, we noticed a snake charmer with two large baskets at the other side of the square, so we went to have a look at him."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 190.648,
      "end": 197.392,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "After a time"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "把时间往前推一点；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "noticed"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是注意到。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 197.742,
      "end": 208.638,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Snake charmer"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是一种传统街头表演者，看起来像用管乐器让蛇移动。这里要说成文化场景，不要说成整个印度的代表。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 208.987,
      "end": 217.123,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "At the other side of the square"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是在广场另一边；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "have a look at him"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是走过去看一看。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 217.473,
      "end": 224.593,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这幅画的重点是 two large baskets 和一个问题：What is in the basket?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 224.943,
      "end": 237.775,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三幅画，是 first glimpse of the snake。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "As soon as he saw us, he picked up a long pipe which was covered with coins and opened one of the baskets."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 238.125,
      "end": 248.829,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "As soon as"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "表示一看见他们，马上行动。动作很快：saw us -> picked up the pipe -> opened one basket。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 249.178,
      "end": 257.37,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "注意"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pipe"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里不是水管，而是 snake charmer 的 wind instrument，一支长长的管乐器。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 257.72,
      "end": 264.808,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Covered with coins"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是上面装饰着硬币。这个细节让 pipe 在画面里很显眼。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 265.158,
      "end": 271.27,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "接着课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "When he began to play a tune, we had our first glimpse of the snake."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 271.62,
      "end": 280.388,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Glimpse"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 brief quick look，第一次短短地看见。蛇不是突然扑出来，而是慢慢从篮子里出现。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 280.738,
      "end": 286.514,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文继续："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It rose out of the basket and began to follow the movements of the pipe."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 286.863,
      "end": 295.171,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里最关键的词是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "movements"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。学生要看到：snake follows movement, not music style。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 295.521,
      "end": 306.201,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四幅画，是 the music switch。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "We were very much surprised when the snake charmer suddenly began to play jazz and modern pop songs."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 306.551,
      "end": 312.831,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "人会听出 style 变了：Indian music, jazz, modern pop songs，耳朵觉得很不一样。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 313.181,
      "end": 318.949,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但是课文马上转折："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The snake, however, continued to 'dance' slowly."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 319.299,
      "end": 328.562,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "However"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 contrast marker，表示“可是”。它提醒你：人觉得音乐变了，可蛇的反应没有变。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 328.912,
      "end": 337.648,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Dance"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "放在引号里，因为它不是像人一样真的跳舞，只是跟着 pipe 的移动慢慢摆动。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 337.998,
      "end": 345.542,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后一句是 punchline："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It obviously could not tell the difference between Indian music and jazz!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 345.892,
      "end": 356.66,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Tell the difference between A and B"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是分辨 A 和 B 的区别。蛇当然分不出印度音乐和爵士乐，因为它并不是在当音乐听众。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 357.01,
      "end": 358.63,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一课最容易误会什么？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 358.98,
      "end": 363.084,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "以为是在说印度很奇怪，或者蛇真的听懂了音乐？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 37,
      "start": 363.434,
      "end": 369.514,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对，所以我们先把 tone 放正。Old Delhi 是一座城市的历史层，不是“落后”的标签。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 38,
      "start": 369.864,
      "end": 373.266,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那这个街头表演怎么讲比较好？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 39,
      "start": 373.616,
      "end": 385.096,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以说它是 travelers 在公共空间里看到的一种 traditional street performance。市场、广场、游客、表演者、音乐和动物都在同一个街头空间里。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 40,
      "start": 385.446,
      "end": 388.296,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "和前面很多课有什么不同？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 41,
      "start": 388.646,
      "end": 399.206,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "前面很多故事在家里、商店、餐桌、医院、车站。这一课更 public, more sensory, more colorful。城市气质不同，不是哪个文化更好。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 42,
      "start": 399.555,
      "end": 401.828,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那 animal welfare 呢？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 43,
      "start": 402.178,
      "end": 414.258,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "很重要。课文记录的是旧教材里的传统表演场景。今天我们可以理解文本，同时知道现代社会会更关注动物保护，不鼓励模仿动物表演。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 44,
      "start": 414.608,
      "end": 417.339,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "科学上，蛇真的听音乐吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 45,
      "start": 417.689,
      "end": 427.88,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "它不是像人一样欣赏旋律。课文已经给了线索："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "follow the movements of the pipe"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
